description: Looking for an incredible, spacious roof deck with amazing 360 degree views, convenient location on a quiet street and ample space with an efficient layout? This is your new home in great condition.  Enjoy the open living room, kitchen layout with a space to work from home and a full staircase to the huge roof deck. The primary bedroom offers great space, natural light and two large closets. The second bedroom is a great guest space or office with another spacious closet. Convenient location a few blocks from West Broadway, multiple T and bus options, Cafe Nero, shops and restaurants all on a quiet side street. Enjoy a nice run/bike to Castle Island and the beach, walk to the hot Seaport District. Direct access to 1 garage parking space! Easy to show with notice. Open house this weekend.
